snippet.title: Lukozer Retro Game Review - 581 - Super Bowl - Commodore 64
snippet.description:
NOTE: Lots of visual glitching in the menu screens due to OBS being a cunt with some C64 games for no reason whatsoever

My review of the Commodore 64 game Super Bowl (AKA Super Bowl XX), released by Ocean in 1986. All the excitement of American Football combined with moving dots around half a screen in near total silence. This is yet another game that Zzap64 raved about and i'm fucked if I can see why...
